      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be verified and documented under a quality management system with version-controlled source code and regression test suite.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 employed under ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Regression test suite of 47 benchmark cases executed prior to simulation campaign; all cases pass within specified tolerances. Version control and audit trail documented."
