      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis is the direct precursor to the relative hemolysis index RH used in the COU acceptance criterion. Pressure rise and velocity field QoIs provide mechanistic support. Relevance confirmed by clinical hemolysis subject-matter expert review."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
