      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at operating conditions spanning the COU envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Geometric similarity confirmed; fluid analog properties matched to physiological blood viscosity range. Validation domain covers all five COU operating points."
    },
    {
