      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, iterative convergence monitoring is sufficient; formal solver error quantification not required.",
      "rationale": "Residuals monitored to below 1e-5 for all equations; mass imbalance below 0.01%. Iterative convergence confirmed adequate for MRL 2 without formal solver error budgeting."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
