      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, peer review of simulation setup is sufficient to address use error without formal independent verification.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second CFD analyst with rotating machinery experience. Boundary conditions, material properties, and solver settings independently verified against documented protocol. No use errors identified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, model form adequacy is addressed through validation evidence rather than independent model form uncertainty analysis.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on prior literature for blood pump flows. Model form uncertainty subsumed within validation comparison uncertainty bands. Formal model form UQ not required at MRL 2."
